text: Kristina Clonan (born 13 April 1998) is an Australian professional racing cyclist. She rode in the women's scratch event at the 2017 UCI Track Cycling World Championships. ==Major results== ;2015 :1st 20px Road Race, Oceania Junior Road Championships :3rd Time Trial, Oceania Junior Road Championships ;2017 :1st 120th Austral Wheel Race :1st Omnium, ITS Melbourne - Hisense Grand Prix :National Track Championships ::1st 20px Madison (with Macey Stewart) ::2nd Team Pursuit :2nd Omnium, ITS Melbourne - DISC Grand Prix ;2018 :Australian National Road Championships ::1st 20px U23 Criterium ::3rd U23 Road Race ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
